Requirements:
- The page must clearly name the claimed vessel and discuss it as a substantive subject of the report's casualty coverage — not as a passing mention or one entry in an aggregate digest's listing of many incidents.
- The page must describe the casualty type ({= casualty_types =}) and indicate that the casualty occurred in {= target_period =}. The casualty's incident date — not the report's publication date — is what carries the timing.
